# AI Customer Support Assistant

## Objective

Build an AI-powered customer support assistant using Prompt Engineering.

## Concepts Used

- Zero-Shot Prompting
- Few-Shot Prompting

## Features

- Complaint Classification
- Sentiment Detection
- Priority Assignment
- Department Routing
- Professional Response Generation

## Technologies

- Python
- Streamlit
- Google Gemini API
- Prompt Engineering

## Run

Install requirements:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run application:

streamlit run app.py